data.title: Michele Lupo
data.meta_description: Michele Lupo. Director: Eine Faust geht nach Westen. Michele Lupo was born on 4 December 1932 in Corleone, Sicily, Italy. He was a director and assistant director, known for Eine Faust geht nach Westen (1981), Ein achtbarer Mann (1972) and Der Stärkste unter der Sonne (1963). He died on 27 June 1989 in Rome, Lazio, Italy.
data.text: Michele Lupo was born on December 4, 1932 in Corleone, Sicily, Italy. He was a director and assistant director, known for Eine Faust geht nach Westen (1981), Ein achtbarer Mann (1972) and Der Stärkste unter der Sonne (1963). He died on June 27, 1989 in Rome, Lazio, Italy.
